E2T9BA.original: ~z~Does it really matter if there's another thing them guys are pissed at us for? I'm sorry, T. Later, bro.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~再被他们记一笔账好像也无所谓了吧？对不起，T。回见，兄弟。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~There was that one marble thing you bought.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~那你是买过一个大理石的嘛。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~ It's only got two exits, T. He should come right out over by where we picked up the chopper.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~一共就俩出口，T。待会儿他就从停机坪那边出来了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Okay, man, let me know if they find Gracie.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~好了，伙计。找到Gracie了就跟我说一声。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You're right. You're right. You're not the one with the problem. I am.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你说得对。你说得对。你没什么问题，我有。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Is he going to take us somewhere or what?
~z~Where these guys from? Other than Dukes, I mean.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~这些傻逼都哪来的？我是说Dukes以外的背景。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~How's he meant to take us to Gracie if he's dead?
~z~Shit. Rocco just forwarded me a photo of Gracie. They've gagged her.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~操。Rocco给我转了张Gracie的照片。她的嘴都被塞住了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~He's going in the parking lot. What's going on?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~他要开进停车场了。怎么回事？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Look! He's stopping. That must be where they're keeping Gracie.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~看！他停车了。那里肯定就是他们关Gracie的地方。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~If it wasn't for me, you'd be selling dime bags on a street corner. I made you.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~要不是我，你还在街上卖毒品呢。是我成就了你。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~T- Tony, what the - what the fuck are you doing?
~z~ Gay guys love that shit, you cliché loving moron.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~基佬们都喜欢那玩意，别念叨刻板印象了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You work in the business, Lou. You should know that club promoters are the first to master all new forms of communication.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你也是搞夜店的，Lou。应该知道夜店推销必须掌握各种新潮的交流方式吧。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~The Ancelotti chopper. Shit, Lou, the old man loved that as much as his daughter.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~Ancelotti的直升机。操，Lou，那老头对它的爱不比女儿少。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Yeah, and she and Evan made you into a junkie. Okay?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~是啊，但她和Evan把你变成了瘾君子，好吗？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~What's he been doing driving anywhere? We give him a moment and call it in if it feels weird.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~他开到哪里都得有动机吗？给他点时间，情况不对就打电话汇报。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~and the fact that we got his baby girl kidnapped in the first place.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~就只有欠他的钱和让他的宝贝女儿被人绑架的事了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~If he sees us we're fucked. What are you doing?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~被他看见我们就完了。你在干什么？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~We stop that fuck's car, we rig his balls to the battery. By the time he smells them cooking we'll know exactly where Gracie's at.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我们逼停这个傻逼，给他的蛋接上汽车电池。等到蛋烤熟了，我们就知道Gracie在哪儿了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I don't know. You want to give him a call and ask him? This was your plan, boss.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我不知道。你想打个电话问问他吗？这是你的计划，老板。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~How the fuck do I know? I guess greed is a powerful motivator.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我他妈怎么知道？只能说人心不足蛇吞象。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~There! He's coming out of the tunnel after all.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~看哪！他还是从隧道这头出来了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Gracie's dead if we lose him. Shit.

E2T9BA.translated: ~z~为什么？因为人们都叫我「基佬」Tony？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Like the fact that he could get he could get his ankles around his ears and ate a lot of mung beans.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~比如他能把脚放到头上，还能吃一大堆绿豆。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I see him. He's crossed over to Alderney. He's coming out the Booth right now.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~看见他了。他跨海来到Alderney了。马上就从隧道里出来了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Let's get this bird on the ground, Lou.
~z~Lou! Lou, what the fuck. He'll see us if we get any closer.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~Lou！Lou，搞毛啊？再靠近就要被发现了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Come on, you dumb Dukes fuck. Take us to her!
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~快点，你个Dukes来的臭傻逼。带我们找到她。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Where's he gone? Where the fuck has he gone?
~z~Okay, okay, I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I just - I just couldn't take it anymore.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~好的，好的。对不起，我很抱歉。我就是...我就是快要崩溃了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Irish like those guys who robbed our bank? They could be the same ones that held me hostage.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~上次抢银行的也是爱尔兰人？说不定就是同一伙人。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Yeah. Giant, veiney, penis-shaped art. At least you made a profit on it. Those were the days.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~是啊。青筋暴起的巨大鸡巴形状的艺术品。至少你还用它赚了一笔。那都是以前了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You never liked her. You never did. You never liked anyone.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你一直不喜欢她，从没喜欢过。你没喜欢过任何人。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You think I want you to kill us? Go over and meet him where he comes out. Over by where we picked this chopper up.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我会让你去找死吗？去对岸出来的地方等他。就是我们上飞机的地方。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Don't you worry, I'm taking a spa day the first opportunity I get.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~别担心，等我有机会，就给自己放个温泉假。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Aw, and what makes you so good, huh?
~z~Unfortunately, I'm a minority too. So fuck you.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~只可惜，我也是少数族裔。所以去你妈的吧。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~What the fuck is wrong with you, you dumb prick? Huh? Get up. Get up, so I can kill you myself. Get up!
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你他妈是怎么了，你个王八蛋？嗯？站起来！站起来，让我亲手宰了你。站起来！

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Where's that red piece of shit, Lou. We're losing him.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~那辆红色破车呢，Lou？我们要跟丢了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Okay. Okay. Why does everything feel weird to me?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~好吧。好吧。我怎么觉得什么都不太对？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~but we need to get the fuck out of here. Call me, okay?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~总之要赶紧离开这里。回头联系，好吗？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~What? Are you just going to follow orders blindly?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~什么？你执行命令都不过脑子的？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Shit, you're right. That fucker told me it was my fault so many times that I'm starting to believe it.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~操，你说得对。那个混账一直说是我的错，搞得我自己都信了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Yeah, they'll have you, me and a mob family to deal with.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~那你、我还有她家的黑手党都不会让他们好受。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~She could be in the trunk of a car in there.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~她可能在哪辆车的后备箱里。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Actually, wait, I can see you driving a pink car, T.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~不过嘛，等下，你开这辆粉色的车我倒是能理解，T。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Okay, but she made you into a useless old queen, too whacked out on blow and pills to notice his business is going to shit.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~但她把你变成了一个没用的老废物，整天只会嗑药，生意一团糟了都不知道。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Don't get so close. He'll know we're on him.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~别靠得太近了，他会发现我们的。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~She should have got suspicious the second anyone expressed an interest in that thing.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~有人对这辆破车感兴趣的时候她就该怀疑了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~What the fuck did I pay for those lessons for. Don't lose him.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我白给你报飞行驾校了。别跟丢他。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Get up you old bastard. Huh? Come on. Let's go find Gracie.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~起来吧，你这个老混球。来，我们一块去找Gracie。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~They're an Irish operation headed by this maniac called Gerald McReary. He's doing time at Alderney State.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~他们是一伙爱尔兰人，带头的是个叫Gerald McReary的疯子，现在在Alderney坐牢。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Look! There he is. He's coming out of the tunnel on the Alderney side.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~快看！他来了。他从Alderney这边的隧道口出来了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~What are you talking about, bro? Where is she?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你到底在说什么啊？她在哪里？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~If he's getting wise it's because you're a tight ass.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~要是被他察觉了，都是因为你太抠门。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Ah, here we go, huh, here we fucking go, huh? Oh, I see it in your eyes. You're embarrassed of me.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~啊，说出来了是吧，哈？这下说出来了，啊？噢，看你的眼神就知道了，你嫌我丢人。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Shit. I just got forwarded a photo of Gracie from the kidnappers. The girl does not look good.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~操。我刚才收到了绑匪发的Gracie的照片。她看起来不太好。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~That image is gonna stick with me. Jesus.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~那画面我一辈子都忘不掉。老天。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Maybe if we concentrate hard enough we can will him to go there.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~没准我们集中精神，就能用意念控制他过去。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I mean, she's not a bad person, okay? She's not a murdering greedy psychopath, like me.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我不是说她是坏人。她不是我这样嗜杀成性的神经病。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Because you owe money to half the city and the other half wants you dead. Paranoia's advised in our situation.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~因为你欠了全城一半人的钱，剩下一半要让你死。这种情况很难不多疑。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I made you a business partner so you'd question things, not just trudge along after me like some drone.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~找你当生意伙伴是让你来提问的，不是像个跟屁虫一样跟着我嗡嗡嗡。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I don't know Alderney well, bro, but I think the big one's Sacramento. Call it in.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我对Alderney不是很熟，兄弟。但我觉得那条大路是Sacramento大道。汇报吧。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~That guy could be anywhere now. Poor little Gracie.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~现在他可能在任何地方。可怜的小Gracie。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~She could be in the trunk of the red piece of shit we're following.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~她也可能在我们追着的红色破车的后备箱里。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Don't lose him, Lou. Where is he?
~z~What would they need a mob bosses daughter for when they got all the bank's money?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~他们都抢了一银行的钱了，还绑架黑帮老大的女儿干嘛？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~They would have checked that. Let's see if he comes out.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~那他们早该打开后备箱了。看看他会不会出来。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Always find a new way of profiting.
~z~Leave the torture to professionals, people in government.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~刑讯逼供的事留给专家，政府的那些人。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Something to do with that pink piece of shit car she had. They think the guy pretended he wanted to buy it.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~肯定和她那辆冒傻气的粉色车子有关。绑匪可能是装成想买这辆车。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Hey, who knows. Bound and gagged might be the look for guido sluts next season.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~谁知道呢。说不定意大利婊子的下一个潮流就是捆绑封口。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You being anti-semitic now? Nice, next you'll call me a fag.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你开始反犹太了？真棒，接下来就该叫我死基佬了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Where's he going? What's he doing in the parking lot?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~他要去哪儿？开进停车场干什么？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I got here as soon as I could, bro.
~z~We are talking about the same Gracie ain't we. Because girl I knew was a foul mouthed whore.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我们说的是同一个Gracie吗？我认识的那位就是个嘴臭的婊子。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I thought you got over that spiritual shit when you stopped dating the yoga instructor.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我还以为跟瑜伽教练分手以后你就忘了什么意念的事了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~She's all heart...you know, if you can get past the accent.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~她很大方...只要你能接受她的口音。
~z~她是我最喜欢的可卡因奴隶。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Then the only thing we've got to worry about with the Ancellotti's is the money we owe them
~z~This a great bit of improvisation, Lou. But I think we should just follow him.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~这段即兴扯得可以，Lou。但我觉得这样跟着他就行。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~And you're not so smart, you dumb junkie fuck.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~那你也没有脑子，嗑药的傻逼人渣！

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Shit. They're onto us. They're going to fucking kill her.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~妈的，被他们发现了。他们他妈的要撕票了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~They got Gracie. She's gone. Evan's dead, now Gracie.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~Gracie被抓了。她失踪了。先是Evan死了，现在Gracie也丢了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Or he could highjack some other car and we'll be sitting here waiting for him with our dicks in our hands.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~他也可以随便抢一辆车，我们只能在这儿握着鸡巴傻等。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Oh yeah, play the minority card. Very clever.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~好啊，开始打少数群体的牌了。真机智。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Poor Gracie. It's such a big fucking city, and she's such a sweet little girl.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~可怜的Gracie。这么大的鬼地方，她又是那么无辜的好女孩。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~That's him, isn't it? He better fucking take us back to Gracie now.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~那个就是他吧？他最好立刻带我们找到Gracie。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Anyways, look at the bright side, at least she's alive.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~总之，往好处想，至少她还活着。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Some guys at war with her father, I guess. I don't know!
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我猜是和她爸有什么过节的人，我不知道！

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Stop driving suspiciously, Lou. He'll get wise to us.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~别开得那么可疑，Lou。会被察觉的。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I don't know, man, but if he was the guy that took her, then he deserves it.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~不知道，兄弟。但他既然是绑匪，那死了活该。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You see me and think "Oh, this is it," this is the moment to put me down, this is the moment when the apprentice takes over, huh?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~心里想的是「噢，是时候了」，是时候把我放倒，是时候轮到小弟上位了，啊？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~There are things that stick with you forever.
~z~I don't think the old man's gonna understand it like that though. Later, T.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~但我觉得那个老头可能不会这么想。回见，T。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Look. He's just there. Lead us back to Gracie, you fucker!
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~看，他在那儿。赶紧带我们找到Gracie，你个王八蛋。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Oh man, you think I'm done. You're not so fucking tough, Luis.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~噢，伙计，你觉得我完蛋了。你他妈还不够格，Luis。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~So what if we lost him, man. They're gonna put in a ransom demand and Ancelotti will pay up. I'll see you soon, ok?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~跟丢他又怎么了，兄弟。他们会索要赎金，Ancelotti肯定会乖乖付钱。我很快会来找你，好吗？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Get wise? What are we in some gumshoe novel now?
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~察觉？我们这是在拍警匪片吗？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Sure. Yeah. Providing they find her and get her back safely.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~当然。没错。只要他们能找到她，把她完好地救回来。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Hey, my dick's in my pants not my hand, T, and it's staying there. Let's just wait to see if he comes out.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~喂，我的鸡巴在裤子里，不在手里，T。也不会掏出来。等着看他出不出来吧。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Look. He's going through the Booth Tunnel.
~z~I'm driving as un-suspiciously as you can when your boss only forked out for a weekend helicopter course.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我已经尽量往不可疑上飞了。你给我报的是周末速成班。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~No. I'm holding you back. I see that now. I see that now.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~不，我连累了你。我现在懂了。我明白了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~He's going into the tunnel. We're fucked.
~z~Great. I like my spinal cord, bro. It would be fucking a shame to lose it.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~真棒。我很爱惜自己的小命的。丢了就可惜了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I hope for our sake they do. See you soon, partner.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~希望他们能快点找到。回头见，搭档。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~In that case, you'd probably think I've got massive sculptures of cocks in my apartment as well.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~这样的话，你是不是还觉得我公寓里有很多鸡巴雕塑啊？

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I bet they have. Bro, I want to gag the bitch most times I see her. Joking, man. I was joking.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~是得塞上。兄弟，每次见到她我都想塞住她的嘴。开玩笑的，兄弟。我开玩笑的。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~Oh yeah, we better leave the country then, T. Vice, Santos, who knows where,
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~是的，我们最好远走高飞，T。罪城、洛圣都，随便什么地方。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~If we pull this off we'll profit - we'll get to keep our spinal cords.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~度过这个难关就能赚钱了，还能把小命保住。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You're the closest thing I've had to a son. I'm sorry, Luis. I love you. Goodbye.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你就像是我的儿子。我很抱歉，Luis。我爱你，再见了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~You yell loud enough he might just hear you.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~你再大声点没准他就能听到了。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~I'll give you some questions alright, T. Just you fucking wait.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我会问你问题的好吗，T。你他妈等着。

E2T9BA.original: ~z~We did our bit. Ancelotti can't hold us responsible no more.
E2T9BA.translated: ~z~我们的工作结了。Ancelotti老头也不能怪咱们了。
